Readme
This is python file
To run this file Download Speech_recognisation and pyaudio packages
to download on terminal type pip install SpeechRecognition and pip install pyaudio

Note* Pyaudio is embedded in this project in SpeechRecognition package, that is why its not shown in imported option, but you have to install both packges

Both packages are Free to use, also has Google Speech Recognition API support
pyaudio is used to connect microphone.
